  "name": "Morrison COU2 — VAD hemolysis credibility assessment (NC-8 clean)",
  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for CFD hemolysis prediction of the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump under ventricular assist device (VAD) conditions. COU2 evaluates whether the computational model can predict absolute hemolysis levels for a Class III VAD device at Model Risk Level 5. The operating envelope is explicitly bounded (flow 2–6 L/min, rotational speed 2000–3500 RPM, hematocrit 35–45%, inlet pressure 5–15 mmHg) and all validation activities are performed within those bounds. Sparse but honest coverage acknowledged. Decision: Accepted with documented rationale.",
